{"type": "article", "id": 45087, "title": "“维秘”内衣甲醛超标，以及，纽约时装周上这些值得一看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-12T02:56:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7048, "name": "纽约时装周"}, {"id": 43989, "name": "United Arrows"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 43990, "name": "Adidas"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 2684, "name": "Mansur Gavriel"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 3530, "name": "Forever 21"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 3531, "name": "维多利亚的秘密"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/201709121006054O17KnHT5LACJrPx.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/gucci-demands-quick-end-to-forever-21-stripe-trademark-lawsuit-claims-10981129/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Gucci 要求法院立刻驳回 Forever 21 早前提出撤销 Gucci “条纹”商标权的要求</strong></a> | 上周五，Gucci 母公司开云集团向美国加州联邦法院提出，因 Forever 21 已经承认抄袭 Gucci 条纹图案，法院应立即驳回 Forever 21 早前提出撤销 Gucci “条纹”商标权的要求。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/469339\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Prada 发布上半年财报，收入下跌 5.7% </strong></a>| 由于欧元增值导致的欧洲游客减少，Prada 在今年上半年收入下跌了 5.7%，至 14 亿欧元。净收入下跌 18%，至 1.16 亿欧元。</p><p><a href=\"http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2017-09-12/doc-ifykuftz6297240.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>维多利亚的秘密被检测出贴身内裤甲醛超标</strong></a> | 近日，上海出入境检验检疫局截获了一批安全性不过关的进口食品和服装，并已集中销毁。其中就包括即将在中国举行大秀的“维多利亚的秘密”以及 Ralph Lauren。销毁的不合格服装共涉及 400 批次，总计约 5.5 万件。5 批 Ralph Lauren 的服装主要涉及 PH 值超标以及儿童服装纽扣、绳带等安全指标不合格，内衣品牌“维多利亚的秘密”发往中国的一批内裤被检测出甲醛超标。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/11/birkenstock-box-barneys/#slide-5\" rel=\"nofollow\">Birkenstock 和 Barneys New York 联手，推出了一家移动的快闪店</a>。这家集装箱快闪店目前位于 Gansevoort 街 90 号，贩售 Birkenstock 鞋以及 Barneys New York 限定款成衣、手提包、配饰系列，将于 9 月 12 日正式开幕。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101214OPzoFw7Ipg6ZEjtW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101213dRfi16cbPBtxHeIV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101209guxLh2fNbmyDBjPr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101209HmpghsWJjR7KlydA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101210tfMO0Egp2sBdxD9F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101211TvaP4FJnbzYQ3ujq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101213YRJvZyifoKEHIQrF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121012139Agy1uNpUf4L6ImE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101216WUYItJDjfRMSXx4o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101217CsAKUV3S1pgQe2Xf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>日本最高端的 Converse 支线 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/converse-addict-2017-autumn\" rel=\"nofollow\">Converse ADDICT</a>，今年秋冬带来了三款全新配色的 Converse 鞋款，包括橄榄色的高筒 Chuck Taylor All Star，以及黑白二色的低筒鞋，该系列定价 16000 日元，将于 10 月 10 日正式登陆日本。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101145qiCzHBmxhb9nKpw8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017091210113531avCQBHqgEXiSh9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101135rRqlx0UieVBQWTHh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666075\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101135ntFQO6SsAVWBN3hx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666075\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101139GFudxKiMXmCperJw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/slam-jam-x-united-arrows-x-adidas-consortium-sneaker-exchange-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Consortium「Sneaker Exchange」特别企划这次带来了 Slam Jam 和 United Arrows 的最新联名系列</a>。</p><p>该系列包括一双用百分百有机纯棉制作的 Campus，以及汽车内饰中常见的灰白色 Alcantara 材质制作的 Gazelle，质感很独特。这个系列将于 9 月 22 日登陆 United Arrows 和 Slam Jam 网店，10 月 7 日起在全球 adidas Consortium 正式上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101047oZQCKv1eBSgc4ny6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101050DpCxYGXlfO83PUTd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101050XJvzCgyqrbEsM7Ix.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121010511iBwMJnyxKPZ6v3R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121010519eIhR4XTiwB7Vtdg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>纽约时装周（9 月 6 日——9 月 13 日）即将落下帷幕，我们也挑选了一些有意思的秀，来看看： </p><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/11/fenty-puma-rihanna-ss18/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rihanna 带来了摩托车主题的走秀</a>。 Fenty Puma 2018 春夏系列的灵感来自摩托车越野赛，有摩托夹克、骑手裤、靴子等多款单品。另外，还在秀场摆放了粉色的砂堆，骑手骑着摩托车腾空跃过，还挺刺激的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101026vkWDFIHbnjod6iyR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101012AVtBYPd90Q1gwu3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101012d1SV4qp0u3a9MN6H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121010129N3cZREde8XIfruC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121010127coDZOqX3nYeGxNE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101013Qi9qLb1IA6B2UGyK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101013sRj3EJdIt9CiQDOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101013BcCat7qF2Qi98GdW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121010130rdLokqMn5YSgzvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101014Tfp3q9d7aeS2lAVm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101014bcuRI56nXZUmsH3z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101015CkQUAShjTtw4zXGi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101015APhnoLgMz5ZWYi3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121010154wdKyfxT7opmFSI1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912101016O3EsF8o2wkYU0KxS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/kate-spade-ss2018-nyfw/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kate Spade</a> 把秀场搬到了纽约的一家生蚝吧，在这里举办了一场“春日茶话会”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100937AbslcaY5VGipqUFE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100938D07RCL9fSm4neyGb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100938h5U1iagqvfuCsbWp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121009365BhMD0zN381JU2Wf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100942zOhjyaktYFL89BgC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>做水桶包包出名的<a href=\"https://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/fall-2017-ready-to-wear-mansur-gavriel/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Mansur Gavriel</a>，在这次的时装周上发布了首个服装系列，由于此次发布的是 2017 秋冬款，所以也在同时采用了“即看即买”的方式。 </p><p>这个系列设计简约，色彩选择丰富，搭配的鞋履和包包也都不错。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100827ZYkb6ERNdFQOIhx3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100827ensX5vCWa9ylhEgZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100827MXAuIUbS3ei71NWj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100828Zptc96qNSkKJDYIC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100828vXkyJEzHYUPCZj7T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100828VNKSfgzFmcsjDMyL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100905IH9Tr7OfFUXPqV4L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100905Sc0V36ydD1MBX9Lk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100905usPTe6C7HJhqtoMd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100906xiWMC9K0NTjVkgUG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100907fHikAD5ry1LYCnWX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100908ArQehTRj81L6Sa4o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100907HxyTJYgAz52t1Oel.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100908NQUfZdc1jeETMP7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121009084t1AMDiN8rh3Rg2I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100908dW0h2PuDlKMtwXI4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100909Wp0oDQlGKFy9a3YX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100910qBC0EFSuwYa2nr4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100910Ld28hnDfKFw9gJtI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100911CGVUIeO8votDNJda.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100911L2elSv5GomWz0PD6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709121009116bwGeJVLZSQ01mhz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100912IgVUljKX8rzdPaoE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170912100912Iop3hNB8PHs0m2gE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/11/fenty-puma-rihanna-ss18/\" rel=\"nofollow\">highsnobiety</a></p>"}